fields.title: University of Virginia Proven To, In Fact, Be The Best University
fields.body:
Although it was never truly a debate, recent reports from almost every top news publisher in the world just came in confirming that UVA is indeed the best institution of high learning to ever exist. Whether it be the academics, student-life, sports scene, downtown Charlottesville, faculty, or the amazing students themselves, there is no doubt that UVA ranks among the best of the best in every category! Understandably, the transfer portal is being flooded after these latest developments as students across the country and globe shoot to attend Mr. Jefferson's university. What great taste they all have!
